### _sp_sv_say_team_player

_sp_sv_say_team_player

Control `say_team` behaviour for players

Values:

- 0: Disable
- 1: Enable (default). Only own team, including team spectators.
- 2: Only own team and all spectators. You will see `(+)` to indicate that more people than intended may receive the message.
- 3: Only own team (no spectators). You will see `(-)` to indicate that less people than intended may receive the message.
